WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.836
The world lived a normal life, filled with safety and peace.

00:00:07.916 --> 00:00:15.752
People enjoyed safety, and children played in harmony.

00:00:15.832 --> 00:00:23.669
In the labs, scientists worked hard to serve humanity.

00:00:23.749 --> 00:00:30.925
Suddenly the ground shook, and a terrifying danger appeared.

00:00:31.005 --> 00:00:38.182
A global invasion began; giant creatures seized our cities.

00:00:38.262 --> 00:00:45.438
These creatures took over the world's landmarks; nowhere was spared.

00:00:45.518 --> 00:00:52.035
Panic spread everywhere and emergency warnings were issued.

00:00:52.115 --> 00:00:59.292
Epidemics spread and hospitals filled with the sick and weary.

00:00:59.372 --> 00:01:07.208
These organisms caused severe skin diseases and painful scars.

00:01:07.288 --> 00:01:15.124
The world's scientists gathered at the research center to face the threat.

00:01:15.204 --> 00:01:23.700
Not alien monsters — but protists that had gone out of control.

00:01:23.780 --> 00:01:30.956
A specialized science team was formed to protect humanity.

00:01:31.036 --> 00:01:36.234
Sadeem — strategic analysis expert

00:01:36.314 --> 00:01:41.511
Atheer — molecular analysis specialist

00:01:41.591 --> 00:01:46.789
Nouray — the team's scientific leader

00:01:46.869 --> 00:01:52.066
Kayser — field defense expert

00:01:52.146 --> 00:01:59.982
The mission began — Sadeem defeats the pathogenic Giardia.

00:02:00.062 --> 00:02:07.899
And Atheer defeats Trichomonas with brilliant scientific skill.

00:02:07.979 --> 00:02:15.815
Nouray rescues civilians while analyzing the dangerous samples.

00:02:15.895 --> 00:02:23.071
And Kayser eliminates Leishmania with advanced techniques.

00:02:23.151 --> 00:02:30.328
Stop! This Paramecium is one of the beneficial protists.

00:02:30.408 --> 00:02:38.244
Not all protists are harmful — they must be protected.

00:02:38.324 --> 00:02:46.820
This is only the beginning... help us bring safety back again!
